on with crgp faculty and students in all phases of defining and conducting its research on global projects crgp offers a three tier membership structure in order to meet the needs of smaller more focused industry members as well as large organizations last modified mon 30 jan 2012 at 15 46 find a lab or organization stay connected itunes icon google+ icon facebook icon twitter icon linkedin icon stanford university school of engineering 475 via ortega stanford california 94305 4121 650.725 1575 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved accreditation info terms of use copyright complaints contact us
